    {
      "para_id": "Q001965.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) When I , Lipit-Eštar , the king of Sumer and Akkad , established justice in Sumer and Akkad , then I dedicated this ( eye-stone ) for Ninlil , lady of the gods , the Inana who created me , my mother who bore me , for my well-being ."
    }
  ],
